author: Bryan, Location: Near Milton Keynes
title: Bryan, Location: Near Milton Keynes
text: Exemplary service both during and after the buying process. After taking delivery, I had a question regarding the hinged lid of the Gewiss Weatherproof Enclosure GW44209 i.e. I could not get the hinge to operate. The member of staff to whom I spoke explained what needed to be done. As a result of his sound advice, I was eventually successful and have decided to keep the Enclosure. Based on my own experience, I cannot fault this company's customer service.
